      .then((data) => {
        console.log(data);
        this.imgUrl = data.hdurl;
        this.explanation = data.imgDescription;
        this.copyright = data.imgAuthor;
        this.title = data.imgTitle;
        this.date = data.imgDate;
      })
      .catch((err) => console.log("Wrong: " + err));
  },
};
